                {
                    "id": 1,
                    "content": "We've trained over 300 veterans and military spouses into software engineers — generating $20M+ in first-year earnings across our alumni network. No tuition. No gimmicks. Just a battle-tested curriculum built by veterans who made the same transition. We've been doing this for over a decade."
